title: I can't see the club i created

replies.body: Me neither it says clubs are back up but the club i created is gone except everyone one in it says i'm still the leader
Is there any way to fix this?

Not at the moment. We're looking into a solution, but I can't give you an ETA on when it will roll out.

Further updates on this issue will be posted on [this thread.](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/miscellaneous/nMisJPK8-clubs-outage-oct-2016) Let me know if you have any questions.
